(4, 1, NULL, '1. Why SRMU', '<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Cutting-Edge Programs</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Choose from a vast array of programs across engineering, management, law, and more, designed to shape you into an expert in your field with the latest industry knowledge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/program-finder\">https://srmu.ac.in/program-finder</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"2\">\r\n		World-Class Infrastructure</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Experience the best of modern learning with state-of-the-art classrooms, advanced labs, and creative studios, providing a perfect environment for academic and practical growth.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/facilities\">https://srmu.ac.in/facilities</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"3\">\r\n		Learn from the Best</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Our experienced faculty are experts in their fields, offering real-world insights that equip you with the skills and knowledge needed to succeed in your career.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/institutes-info\">https://srmu.ac.in/institutes-info</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"4\">\r\n		Industry Connections</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	SRMU&rsquo;s strong partnerships with top companies open doors to valuable internships and placement opportunities, ensuring you&#39;re ready to launch your career.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/recognition-approvals\">https://srmu.ac.in/recognition-approvals</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"5\">\r\n		Holistic Growth</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	From sports to clubs and leadership opportunities, SRMU offers countless ways to develop your skills, boost your confidence, and shape your future.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/events\">https://srmu.ac.in/events</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"6\">\r\n		Exciting Scholarships Schemes</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Whether you&#39;re a top performer, a sports enthusiast, or from an economically weaker section, SRMU provides scholarships to ensure financial constraints don&#39;t stop your dreams.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"7\">\r\n		Placement Excellence</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	SRMU has strong connections with leading companies across various sectors, offering students exclusive access to internships, training, and job opportunities.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/placement-overview\">https://srmu.ac.in/placement-overview</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"8\">\r\n		Comprehensive Skill Development</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	SRMU offers career-oriented training programs, workshops, and soft skills development to make students industry-ready and enhance their employability.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/\">https://srmu.ac.in</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Alumni Network Support</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	The extensive SRMU alumni network serves as a valuable resource for mentorship and job referrals, helping students navigate their career paths successfully.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/\">https://srmu.ac.in</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"10\">\r\n		<strong><em>Admission Enquiry</em></strong> <a href=\"https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li value=\"11\">\r\n		<strong>Apply Online </strong><a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 'rich_text', '{\"type\":\"rich_text\"}', 0, 0, '2025-04-26 15:57:34', '2025-04-26 19:24:00'),
