(19, 1, NULL, '3.	Admissions Information', '<p>\r\n	<strong>3. Admission Information </strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Overview</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Admissions at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University are open for a wide range of undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral programs across disciplines. With an industry-aligned curriculum, experienced faculty, modern infrastructure, and strong placement support, SRMU offers a seamless admission process focused on student success and holistic development.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/admission-overview\">https://srmu.ac.in/admission-overview</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"2\">\r\n		How to Apply</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Applying to Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University is quick and simple! Just visit <a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/login\" target=\"_new\">https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/login</a>, register with your basic details, fill out the online application form, upload the required documents, and submit the application fee. Once submitted, our admission team will connect with you for the next steps, including counseling and document verification. Start your journey today!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know morel: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/how-to-apply\">https://srmu.ac.in/how-to-apply</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"3\">\r\n		Fee Structure</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	At <strong>Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), Lucknow</strong>, the fee structure is designed to be <strong>affordable, transparent, and student-friendly</strong>, offering excellent value for quality education across all programs. he annual tuition fee varies based on the course and specialization:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Undergraduate Programs:</strong> Starting from â‚¹32,000 to â‚¹1,55,000 per year</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Postgraduate Programs:</strong> Starting from â‚¹37,000 to â‚¹1,60,000 per year</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Diploma &amp; Polytechnic Courses:</strong> Starting from â‚¹30,000 per year</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Ph.D. Programs:</strong> As per UGC norms with flexible payment options</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Special Subsidized Fee Structure for Students from Bihar and Select Regions</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ“Œ <em>Scholarships up to 100%</em> are available for meritorious students, national exam qualifiers, and based on CUET/JEE/CLAT/CAT scores.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;\">\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/fee-structure\">https://srmu.ac.in/fee-structure</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"4\">\r\n		Scholarship Schemes</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	At <strong>Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), Lucknow</strong>, we believe that financial constraints should never hold back talent. Our diverse <strong>scholarship schemes</strong> are designed to support meritorious, deserving, and hardworking students:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Merit-Based Scholarships</strong><br />\r\n	Up to <strong>100% tuition fee waiver</strong> based on qualifying exam scores and academic performance.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>National Entrance Exam-Based Scholarships</strong><br />\r\n	Special benefits for students with valid scores in <strong>JEE, CUET, CAT, CLAT, MAT, GATE</strong>, and other national exams.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>CUET Score-Based Scholarship</strong><br />\r\n	Attractive fee waivers for students applying through <strong>CUET (UG/PG)</strong> with strong scores.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Career Progression Scholarship</strong><br />\r\n	Exclusive benefits for students from <strong>Ramswaroop Group institutions</strong> pursuing higher studies at SRMU.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Referral Scholarship</strong><br />\r\n	Incentives for students referred by <strong>SRMU alumni, faculty, or enrolled students</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Sports Excellence Scholarship</strong><br />\r\n	For students with achievements at <strong>state or national level sports competitions</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Defense &amp; Paramilitary Personnel Scholarship</strong><br />\r\n	Fee concession for children of <strong>serving or retired Armed Forces personnel</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	ðŸ”¹ <strong>Need-Based Financial Assistance</strong><br />\r\n	Support for students from <strong>economically weaker sections (EWS)</strong> upon verification.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:35.45pt;\">\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"5\">\r\n		Admission FAQs</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	At SRMU, applying is quick and easy through our online portal. We offer a wide range of UG, PG, Diploma, and Ph.D. programs across disciplines. Admissions are based on merit and national entrance exams like JEE, CUET, CLAT, and CAT. Students can avail multiple scholarships, hostel facilities, and strong placement support. For queries, call us at <strong>983890466</strong> or visit <a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/login\" target=\"_new\">studentportal.srmu.ac.in</a>.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/admission-faqs\">https://srmu.ac.in/admission-faqs</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"6\">\r\n		<strong><em>Admission Enquiry</em></strong> <a href=\"https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li value=\"7\">\r\n		<strong>Apply Online </strong><a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 'rich_text', '{\"type\":\"rich_text\"}', 0, 0, '2025-04-26 19:43:28', '2025-04-26 19:43:28'),
(20, 1, NULL, '4. Campus Facilities', '<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Facilities</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Academic Facilities:<br />\r\n		SRMU provides state-of-the-art academic infrastructure to foster innovation and excellence. The university is equipped with <strong>smart classrooms</strong>, <strong>advanced laboratories</strong>, <strong>high-performance computing systems</strong>, <strong>departmental libraries</strong>, and a <strong>central digital library</strong> with access to national and international journals. Facilities like the <strong>AI Centre of Excellence</strong>, <strong>SWAYAM-NPTEL Learning Centre</strong>, and dedicated <strong>research labs</strong> support hands-on learning and academic research. Frequent workshops, seminars, and guest lectures by industry experts enrich the academic experience.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:78.0pt;\">\r\n	Click to know more:&nbsp; <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/facilities\">https://srmu.ac.in/facilities</a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sports Facilities:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	At SRMU, sports are an integral part of student life. The university offers excellent facilities for both indoor and outdoor games including <strong>cricket, football, basketball, volleyball, badminton, table tennis</strong>, and more. A dedicated <strong>sports complex and gymnasium</strong> promotes physical fitness and well-being. Students regularly participate in inter-college and national-level tournaments, and annual sports events like <strong>ULLAS</strong> add to the excitement. SRMU nurtures team spirit, leadership, and a healthy competitive attitude through its vibrant sports culture.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:78.0pt;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Click to know more:&nbsp; <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/facilities\">https://srmu.ac.in/facilities</a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Cafeteria &amp; Eating Joints:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	SRMU offers a vibrant and hygienic dining experience through its well-maintained <strong>central cafeteria</strong> and multiple <strong>on-campus food joints</strong>. Students can enjoy a variety of wholesome meals, snacks, and beverages catering to different tastes and dietary preferences. From traditional Indian dishes to fast food options, the campus ensures both quality and variety. With clean seating areas and a relaxed atmosphere, these dining spaces serve as ideal spots for students to unwind, connect, and recharge during their academic day.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:78.0pt;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Click to know more:&nbsp; <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/facilities\">https://srmu.ac.in/facilities</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"2\">\r\n		Trasnportaion</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	SRMU provides safe and reliable transportation facilities for students and staff. The university operates a fleet of well-maintained buses that cover major routes across <strong>Lucknow and nearby regions</strong>, ensuring hassle-free commuting. All vehicles are equipped with safety features and are operated by trained drivers. The transportation system is designed to be punctual, comfortable, and affordable, making daily travel to and from the campus smooth and convenient for everyone.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/transportation\">https://srmu.ac.in/transportation</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"3\">\r\n		Clubs &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Clubs are vibrant communities within an institution that foster a sense of belonging and offer students opportunities to pursue their passions outside the classroom. They cater to a wide range of interests, from sports and arts to literature and social causes, encouraging personal growth, skill development, and collaboration. Being part of a club allows students to connect with like-minded individuals, gain leadership experience, and contribute to the campus culture, creating a balanced and enriching college experience.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/clubs\">https://srmu.ac.in/clubs</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"4\">\r\n		Events</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Events enrich campus life by bringing students together for learning, fun, and growth. From workshops to cultural fests, they offer opportunities to showcase talents, build skills, and connect with others, enhancing both personal and academic experiences.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/events\">https://srmu.ac.in/events</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"5\">\r\n		Student Senate</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	The Student Senate is a student-led body that represents the interests and concerns of the student community. It serves as a bridge between students and the administration, organizing events, voicing student opinions, and advocating for improvements on campus. Being part of the Senate helps students develop leadership, communication, and decision-making skills.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/student-senate\">https://srmu.ac.in/student-senate</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"6\">\r\n		Student Corner</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	The Student Corner is a designated space where students can gather, relax, and engage in various activities. It serves as a hub for social interaction, collaboration, and sharing ideas, offering a comfortable environment for students to unwind, study, or participate in informal events. It&rsquo;s a place that fosters a sense of community and belonging on campus.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/student-corner\">https://srmu.ac.in/student-corner</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"7\">\r\n		<strong><em>Admission Enquiry</em></strong> <a href=\"https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li value=\"8\">\r\n		<strong>Apply Online </strong><a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 'rich_text', '{\"type\":\"rich_text\"}', 0, 0, '2025-04-26 19:44:07', '2025-04-26 19:44:07'),
(21, 1, NULL, '5- Scholarship Schemes', '<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Merit Based: A Marks-Based Merit Scholarship is awarded based on a student&#39;s performance in their qualification exam, such as Intermediate or previous degree exams. The scholarship recognizes academic excellence and provides financial assistance to students with high marks. Eligibility is determined by the percentage or grade achieved, with higher marks leading to greater scholarship opportunities.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"2\">\r\n		National Entrance Score Based: A National Entrance Score-Based Scholarship is awarded based on a student&#39;s performance in a national entrance exam. It recognizes top scorers and provides financial support to help with tuition fees and other educational expenses. Eligibility is determined by the score achieved in the exam, and the scholarship amount can vary depending on the score range.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"3\">\r\n		CUET Score Based: A CUET Score-Based Scholarship is awarded to students based on their performance in the Common University Entrance Test (CUET). This scholarship recognizes high scorers and helps cover tuition fees or other academic expenses. Eligibility is determined by the student&#39;s CUET score, with higher scores typically earning greater financial support.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"4\">\r\n		SRMUSET: â€‹Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU) offers scholarships based on performance in the SRMUSET (SRMU Scholarship Entrance Test). This test is for students interested in undergraduate (except B.Ed. and LL.B.) and integrated programs.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"5\">\r\n		Career Progression: Students from Ramswaroop Group institutions pursuing higher studies at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU) are eligible for exclusive scholarship benefits aimed at supporting their academic and career progression. These scholarships are designed to reward their academic achievements and provide financial assistance, making higher education more accessible.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"6\">\r\n		Referral Based: Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU) offers a <strong>Referral-Based Scholarship</strong> to encourage students from Ramswaroop Group institutions to pursue higher studies at SRMU. This scholarship provides a fee concession for students who are referred by existing SRMU students or staff members. To qualify, the referring individual must be a current student or staff member of SRMU. This initiative aims to foster a sense of community and support among students while making quality education more accessible.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"7\">\r\n		Ward of Defense Personnel: SRMU offers a <strong>Special Scholarship</strong> for the wards of defense personnel, reflecting their commitment to honoring those who serve the nation.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"8\">\r\n		Sportsperson: SRMU offers specialized scholarships to recognize and support exceptional talent in various fields, including sports. These scholarships are designed to encourage students to excel in their chosen sports while pursuing higher education.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		EWS: SRMU offers a scholarship for students from the Economically Weaker Section (EWS) to help cover tuition and academic expenses. This scholarship ensures that financial constraints don&#39;t hinder access to quality education. Eligible students can apply by submitting the required EWS documentation during admission.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	Click to know more: <a href=\"https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme\">https://srmu.ac.in/scholarship-scheme</a></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"10\">\r\n		<strong><em>Admission Enquiry</em></strong> <a href=\"https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://admissionenquiry.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li value=\"11\">\r\n		<strong>Apply Online </strong><a href=\"https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/\"><strong>https://studentportal.srmu.ac.in/</strong></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 'rich_text', '{\"type\":\"rich_text\"}', 0, 0, '2025-04-26 19:44:40', '2025-04-26 19:58:06'),
(22, 1, NULL, '6. Contact Support', '<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Placement Cell</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	For any placement-related queries, feel free to reach out to our Placement Cell at director.placement@srmu.ac.in.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	We&#39;re here to assist you with career opportunities and guidance!</p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"2\">\r\n		Exam Cell</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n	For any exam-related queries, please contact our Exam Cell at coe@srmu.ac.in.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	We&rsquo;re here to help with all your examination needs!</p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha;\">\r\n	<li value=\"3\">\r\n		Admission Office</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tollfree</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	For admission-related inquiries at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), you can contact the Admission Toll-Free Number: <strong>1800 102 6004</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	This helpline is available to assist you with information regarding programs, application procedures, and other admission-related queries.â€‹</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Whatspp</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	For admission-related inquiries at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), you can contact the Admission WhatsApp number:â€‹ <strong>â€‹+91-9120007948</strong>â€‹</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;\">\r\n	This contact is available for assistance with application processes, program details, and other admission-related queries.â€‹</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Helpline</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;\">\r\n	For admission-related inquiries at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), you can contact the Admission Helpline: <strong>+91-983890466</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Email</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:70.9pt;\">\r\n	â€‹For admission-related inquiries at Shri Ramswaroop Memorial University (SRMU), you can contact the Admissio